            "Maintained a Monorepo codebase with Expo.",
            "Implemented typesafe tRPC backend functions and managed Prisma migrations.",
        ],
    },
    {
        role: "Senior Software Engineer",
        company: "Sysco LABS",
        location: "Colombo, Sri Lanka",
        date: "Mar 2023 – Jul 2024",
        description: [
            "Led development of reusable front-end components and optimized microservices for Sysco Shop, a global food-service platform with 10,000+ users.",
            "Optimized Backend for frontend (BFF) and GraphQL queries, reducing load times by 40% across AWS deployments.",
