            "Developed customized components using native DOM elements and optimized front-end performance via code splitting and lazy loading.",
        ],
    },
    {
        role: "Software Engineer",
        company: "Haulmatic Technologies",
        location: "Colombo, Sri Lanka",
        date: "Oct 2020 – Feb 2022",
        description: [
            "Developed full-stack modules for a supply chain automation platform used by exporters, importers, and freight forwarders.",
            "Created responsive Angular user interfaces and Spring Boot microservices deployed on GCP Kubernetes.",
            "Built real-time transport tracking features using Flutter, improving status update efficiency.",
        ],
    },
    {
        role: "Associate Software Engineer",
        company: "Itechro Ltd",
        location: "Colombo, Sri Lanka",
        date: "Mar 2020 – Oct 2020",
        description: [
            "Delivered a credit application system for Sampath Bank processing 5,000+ monthly applications.",
            "Developed a POS system for Healthguard Pharma (React + MySQL).",
        ],
